title: 1 BR at West Side Flats - Live by the River
posting_body: ['1 Bedroom/1 Bath | $1,294-$1,366 month | 646-719 sq ft', 'Call or email for more information:', 'show contact info', '| <URL>', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', '60 Mbps Internet for each unit – no setup needed; just move in', 'Large granite kitchen islands', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Washer/dryer in-unit', 'Lighted ceiling fans in every master bedroom', 'Programmable thermostats', 'Walk-out patios/decks *', 'Glass bump-out windows *', 'Vinyl wood-look plank flooring', '*In select units', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', 'NOW OPEN: Starbucks and Catrinas Cerveza & Mexican Grill', 'On-site management', '24/7 emergency maintenance', 'Complimentary coffee bar in lobby', 'Club room with full-sized kitchen', 'Underground heated parking: starting at $120/month', 'Storage lockers', 'Bike storage', '24/7 fitness center with cardio, free weight, and strength machines', 'Indoor/outdoor pool', 'Downtown panoramic pool views', 'Indoor and outdoor seating', 'Changing room/shower', 'Patio grill station', 'Free WiFi', 'Concierge Services', 'Dry cleaning', 'Grocery delivery', 'Pet services', 'House cleaning service', 'Skyline Lounge', 'Outdoor fire pit and seating', 'Grilling station', 'Large exterior TV', 'River & skyline views', 'Indoor/outdoor fireplace', 'Pool table', 'Large flat screen TVs', 'Free WiFi', 'We are a Pet Friendly Community!', 'We require a $300.00 refundable pet deposit and $50/month for dogs and $25/month for cats.', 'Limit 2 animals per apartment, 70 lb combined pet weight limit.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'We are located near the High Bridge Dog Park on 59 Randolph Ave, St Paul, MN (1.7 mi walk from West Side Flats)', '**** Non Smoking Community****', '*Rents subject to change daily, please contact us for the most updated pricing', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
